data.title: Shawn Yue in Levi's® Cool Jeans / Levi's® Keep Cool ?? -????
data.description:
This spring, Levi's® is launching COOLMAX® and a collective range of COOL JEANS, an innovative denim collection specifically constructed to combat sweltering hot weather. With Levi's® COOL JEANS, everyone, everywhere has the opportunity to wear denim and non-denim styles year-round, regardless of the temperature. 

Engineered for comfort and woven with specialized fibers that create a cooling effect, these looks help adjust the body's temperature to maintain comfort amidst the summer heat, to KEEP you COOL from inside out. Hong Kong actor Shawn Yue(余文樂) demonstrated his persistence in pursuing own aspirations in the light-weighted and breathable Levi's® COOL JEANS.

data.title: Levi's 2014 Lunar New Year collection: New looks for a new year.
data.description:
The Levi's® 2014 Lunar New Year (Year of Horse) collection takes the pioneers of today on a journey that starts with the Modern Frontier, a belief that the wisdom gleaned from our past will allow for greater possibilities ahead. Be bold. Brave. Daring. 

The headline 'Fortune Favors the Fearless' is a reminder to take risks, seek truth and move into the future with optimism and enthusiasm.
Steeped in heritage and iconography, yet festive and future-forward, our Lunar New Year collection incorporates the traditional colors of the holiday: red and gold, for luck and prosperity. Design brings together a fresh mix of eclectic and iconic. Prints and scale are reworked with unconventional placement. Metallic studs shine in heritage classics. Hidden details surprise and delight; contrast comes in the form of tonal panels and embroidered embellishment. Rocker, refined.

FORTUNE FAVORS THE FEARLESS. GO FORTH.

asset.title: Match Made In Levi's: Rosario Baeza + Lucas Araujo
asset.description:
Rosario Baeza toca el violín desde los ocho años, cuando se enamoró de su expresividad. Tras una vida tocando, el instrumento es ya una extensión de su cuerpo, pero también de su mente y su espíritu.
Cautivado por la danza contemporánea, Lucas Araujo comenzó a moverse sobre escenarios a los 15 años, para con el
tiempo recorrer Sudamérica y Europa. Los pies pueden llevarte más lejos cuando siguen al corazón. Al reunirlos se complementan, encuentran una nueva expresión. Juntos forman un #MatchMadeInLevis.

data.title: Introducing the Levi's® 505™C
data.description:
Born in 1967, the 505™ jean came of age in the 70s New York punk scene. Pop artists, graffiti writers and rock stars all wore them, tore them and thrashed them. 

Now we introduce the 505™C, a modernized and remastered take on the ageless 505™ fit.
